[
  {
    "text": "The humans. We're not all bad and",
    "start": 0.16,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "foolish dear.",
    "start": 3.439,
    "duration": 8.681
  },
  {
    "text": "Very well. Then you can die with them.",
    "start": 5.759,
    "duration": 6.361
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 12.33,
    "duration": 3.269
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me go.",
    "start": 13.519,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Time to wipe the slate clean. Starting",
    "start": 15.599,
    "duration": 7.641
  },
  {
    "text": "with you with no.",
    "start": 18.48,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Nice job, dear monster. You sure got him",
    "start": 25.92,
    "duration": 5.119
  },
  {
    "text": "and good.",
    "start": 29.039,
    "duration": 6.841
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You haven't seen anything yet.",
    "start": 31.039,
    "duration": 4.841
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You're coming with me.",
    "start": 40.559,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Help.",
    "start": 42.96,
    "duration": 6.04
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No. Get back here.",
    "start": 44.879,
    "duration": 4.121
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Dear monster.",
    "start": 53.52,
    "duration": 6.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Brother,",
    "start": 56.64,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> what do we do, dear monster?",
    "start": 61.92,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We get your brother back before.",
    "start": 63.6,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What was that?",
    "start": 67.84,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Nothing good",
    "start": 69.28,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> the snow. It's melting.",
    "start": 74.0,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": ">> That's a good thing, right?",
    "start": 76.88,
    "duration": 5.559
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait.",
    "start": 79.439,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "This isn't good.",
    "start": 91.84,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to the rod, dear monster.",
    "start": 96.64,
    "duration": 8.92
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Let me go.",
    "start": 101.28,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Insolent little ape. If I do that, you'd",
    "start": 106.24,
    "duration": 8.64
  },
  {
    "text": "fall and go splat. Wouldn't want that.",
    "start": 110.799,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, would we?",
    "start": 114.88,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh?",
    "start": 117.439,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What is this stuff?",
    "start": 119.04,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It's here earlier than I expected. We're",
    "start": 121.68,
    "duration": 6.119
  },
  {
    "text": "going down.",
    "start": 124.479,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> My head.",
    "start": 130.64,
    "duration": 6.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh? Well, what happened to the forest?",
    "start": 132.879,
    "duration": 6.881
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 137.34,
    "duration": 6.34
  },
  {
    "text": "The rot happened. Thanks to you and your",
    "start": 139.76,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": "friend, I couldn't save it.",
    "start": 143.68,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You're a monster.",
    "start": 146.56,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No, I'm not the monster you think I am.",
    "start": 147.92,
    "duration": 7.679
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What do you mean? You tried to kill the",
    "start": 153.36,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "deer.",
    "start": 155.599,
    "duration": 4.321
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It's true, but only because he got in my",
    "start": 156.8,
    "duration": 6.159
  },
  {
    "text": "way. My real goal was always to protect",
    "start": 159.92,
    "duration": 6.24
  },
  {
    "text": "the forest, no matter the cost.",
    "start": 162.959,
    "duration": 5.761
  },
  {
    "text": "Protected from what?",
    "start": 166.16,
    "duration": 5.96
  },
  {
    "text": ">> From him,",
    "start": 168.72,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": ">> friends. Stay behind me.",
    "start": 173.519,
    "duration": 5.521
  },
  {
    "text": "It's cute that you think you can save",
    "start": 176.72,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "them. All life in this forest will",
    "start": 179.04,
    "duration": 7.6
  },
  {
    "text": "succumb to me. The rot bear monster.",
    "start": 182.48,
    "duration": 7.44
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Rott bear monster. What is it you want?",
    "start": 186.64,
    "duration": 6.239
  },
  {
    "text": ">> The cycle of life and death is out of",
    "start": 189.92,
    "duration": 8.36
  },
  {
    "text": "balance. I will set things right.",
    "start": 192.879,
    "duration": 5.401
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 206.28,
    "duration": 3.349
  },
  {
    "text": ">> This is bad. Any ideas here, monster?",
    "start": 213.519,
    "duration": 6.961
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yes. Run.",
    "start": 216.56,
    "duration": 7.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Rock legion after them.",
    "start": 220.48,
    "duration": 6.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Run all you like, dear monster.",
    "start": 223.68,
    "duration": 8.44
  },
  {
    "text": "You are only prolonging the inevitable.",
    "start": 227.36,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": ">> So you're saying this is our fault?",
    "start": 234.959,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yes. The rot bear monsters only here",
    "start": 237.28,
    "duration": 6.4
  },
  {
    "text": "because you humans refuse to perish.",
    "start": 240.879,
    "duration": 7.041
  },
  {
    "text": ">> So wipe us out to save your own skin.",
    "start": 243.68,
    "duration": 7.279
  },
  {
    "text": ">> So selfish. You don't see the bigger",
    "start": 247.92,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "picture. Your presence here has drawn",
    "start": 250.959,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "the rock bear out. It's hopeless. You've",
    "start": 253.84,
    "duration": 7.399
  },
  {
    "text": "doomed us all to extinction.",
    "start": 256.799,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Keep going, friends. Back to your",
    "start": 265.04,
    "duration": 3.52
  },
  {
    "text": "campsite.",
    "start": 266.96,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": ">> But what about you?",
    "start": 268.56,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I can take care of myself. Go.",
    "start": 270.32,
    "duration": 7.04
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Listen to the deer, guys. Let's go.",
    "start": 273.12,
    "duration": 7.92
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You want a piece of me? Well, then come",
    "start": 277.36,
    "duration": 7.24
  },
  {
    "text": "and get salmon.",
    "start": 281.04,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Well done. I'd expect nothing less from",
    "start": 291.44,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "the legendary DM monster.",
    "start": 294.479,
    "duration": 7.201
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Your reign of terror ends here.",
    "start": 297.6,
    "duration": 7.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I doubt that the rot will seep down into",
    "start": 301.68,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "each and every pore of this oursed place",
    "start": 304.88,
    "duration": 6.4
  },
  {
    "text": "until not a single trace of life",
    "start": 308.4,
    "duration": 4.079
  },
  {
    "text": "remains.",
    "start": 311.28,
    "duration": 5.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Not if I can help it.",
    "start": 312.479,
    "duration": 4.121
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 322.43,
    "duration": 3.159
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 329.57,
    "duration": 8.03
  },
  {
    "text": "You're wrong. You know",
    "start": 335.039,
    "duration": 5.121
  },
  {
    "text": ">> h about what?",
    "start": 337.6,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It's not hopeless. Not when the deer",
    "start": 340.16,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "monster is still here to protect us.",
    "start": 342.4,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Even after everything that mang beast",
    "start": 345.039,
    "duration": 5.761
  },
  {
    "text": "has put you through, you still have",
    "start": 347.919,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "faith in him.",
    "start": 350.8,
    "duration": 5.119
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I do. And I have faith in you, too.",
    "start": 351.919,
    "duration": 5.441
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Me?",
    "start": 355.919,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yeah. You care about the forest, too.",
    "start": 357.36,
    "duration": 6.24
  },
  {
    "text": "You just have a funny way of showing it.",
    "start": 360.72,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Deep down, you're not a monster.",
    "start": 363.6,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Oh,",
    "start": 366.56,
    "duration": 3.199
  },
  {
    "text": ">> but it's not enough for me to believe",
    "start": 368.08,
    "duration": 4.78
  },
  {
    "text": "it. You have to prove it.",
    "start": 369.759,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 372.86,
    "duration": 6.619
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah,",
    "start": 376.479,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> monster over here.",
    "start": 380.639,
    "duration": 4.641
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Come on. This way,",
    "start": 383.039,
    "duration": 5.201
  },
  {
    "text": ">> friends.",
    "start": 385.28,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "It's no use. Close your eyes. You don't",
    "start": 388.24,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "need to see this.",
    "start": 391.6,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Monster,",
    "start": 393.759,
    "duration": 7.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I'm going to enjoy this.",
    "start": 396.479,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Please let him go.",
    "start": 404.56,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I don't think so. The rod consumes us",
    "start": 407.28,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": "all. Starting with him.",
    "start": 410.4,
    "duration": 5.919
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Put him down, Pear.",
    "start": 413.84,
    "duration": 7.079
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What the could it be?",
    "start": 416.319,
    "duration": 4.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Need a hand.",
    "start": 427.039,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "But why? You're right. The humans are",
    "start": 429.68,
    "duration": 8.48
  },
  {
    "text": "not all bad after all.",
    "start": 433.759,
    "duration": 7.84
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Why, you little brat. You will all rot.",
    "start": 438.16,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Dear monster, there's only one option.",
    "start": 441.599,
    "duration": 5.681
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you ready?",
    "start": 444.96,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Ready? This is going to hurt him more",
    "start": 447.28,
    "duration": 7.96
  },
  {
    "text": "than us. Come on.",
    "start": 450.88,
    "duration": 4.36
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you doing? Are you mad? No,",
    "start": 460.96,
    "duration": 9.0
  },
  {
    "text": "that's not it. We just",
    "start": 464.88,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 470.16,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 480.53,
    "duration": 7.15
  },
  {
    "text": "So, what do you say, truce?",
    "start": 482.8,
    "duration": 8.029
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 487.68,
    "duration": 3.149
  }
]